title: True Story, Swear To God V2
description:
Issues 1-13 of 'True Story, Swear To God' V2

Image Comics, 2006-2010, 26-36 pages

Written and Illustrated by Tom Beland

As evidenced by the title, it's the true story of a romance between Tom, an aspiring cartoonist who lives in California and Lily, a radio personality from Puerto Rico. It follows their first meeting, to encounters with each others families, and through the difficulties of a long-distance relationship.
